zim: zim (A desktop wiki and outliner)
zim:
zim: Zim is a WYSIWYG text editor written in Gtk2-Perl It aims to bring
zim: the concept of a wiki to your desktop. Every page is saved as a text
zim: file with wiki markup. Pages can contain links to other pages, and
zim: are saved automatically. Creating a new page is as easy as linking
zim: to a non-existing page. This tool is intended to keep track of TODO
zim: lists or to serve as a personal scratch book.
zim:
zim:
